data.name: Draken, the Drifting Cloud
data.notes: "Draken, the Drifting Cloud" floats around in the tropical areas out in the Primordia Waters between Primordia and Sylvalum. Starts high above the small mountain on the largest tropical island and descends from there. Has two smaller Balaena on either side. Big enough to be mistaken for the shadow of a cloud.
